Class PololuVirtualCat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robodoot.roboapp.VirtualCat
      • com.robodoot.roboapp.PololuVirtualCat

  • public class PololuVirtualCat
extends VirtualCat
    A concrete implementation of the VirtualCat interface which controls the cat by communicating only with the Pololu (no Arduino).
